make.name: make
make.short_desc: Create a new collection instance if the value isn't one already.

has.name: has
has.short_desc: Determine if an item exists in the collection by key.

get.name: get
get.short_desc: Get an item from the collection by key.

all.name: all
all.short_desc: Get all of the items in the collection.

put.name: put
put.short_desc: Put an item in the collection by key.

first.name: first
first.short_desc: Get the first item from the collection.

last.name: last
last.short_desc: Get the last item from the collection.

shift.name: shift
shift.short_desc: Get and remove the first item from the collection.

prepend.name: prepend
prepend.short_desc: Push an item onto the beginning of the collection.

push.name: push
push.short_desc: Push an item onto the end of the collection.

pop.name: pop
pop.short_desc: Get and remove the last item from the collection.

forget.name: forget
forget.short_desc: Remove an item from the collection by key.

reduce.name: reduce
reduce.short_desc: Reduce the collection to a single value.

each.name: each
each.short_desc: Execute a callback over each item.

map.name: map
map.short_desc: Run a map over each of the items.

transform.name: transform
transform.short_desc: Transform each item in the collection using a callback.

filter.name: filter
filter.short_desc: Run a filter over each of the items.

sort.name: sort
sort.short_desc: Sort through each item with a callback.

sortBy.name: sortBy
sortBy.short_desc: Sort the collection using the given Closure.

values.name: values
values.short_desc: Reset the keys on the underlying array.

fetch.name: fetch
fetch.short_desc: Fetch a nested element of the collection.

flatten.name: flatten
flatten.short_desc: Get a flattened array of the items in the collection.

collapse.name: collapse
collapse.short_desc: Collapse the collection items into a single array.

merge.name: merge
merge.short_desc: Merge the collection with the given items.

diff.name: diff
diff.short_desc: Diff the collection with the given items.

intersect.name: intersect
intersect.short_desc: Intersect the collection with the given items.

unique.name: unique
unique.short_desc: Return only unique items from the collection array.

splice.name: splice
splice.short_desc: Splice portion of the underlying collection array.

take.name: take
take.short_desc: Take the first or last {$limit} items.

lists.name: lists
lists.short_desc: Get an array with the values of a given key.

implode.name: implode
implode.short_desc: Concatenate values of a given key as a string.

isEmpty.name: isEmpty
isEmpty.short_desc: Determine if the collection is empty or not.

toArray.name: toArray
toArray.short_desc: Get the collection of items as a plain array.

toJson.name: toJson
toJson.short_desc: Get the collection of items as JSON.

getIterator.name: getIterator
getIterator.short_desc: Get an iterator for the items.

count.name: count
count.short_desc: Count the number of items in the collection.

offsetExists.name: offsetExists
offsetExists.short_desc: Determine if an item exists at an offset.

offsetGet.name: offsetGet
offsetGet.short_desc: Get an item at a given offset.

offsetSet.name: offsetSet
offsetSet.short_desc: Set the item at a given offset.

offsetUnset.name: offsetUnset
offsetUnset.short_desc: Unset the item at a given offset.

__toString.name: __toString
__toString.short_desc: Convert the collection to its string representation.
